222
00:15:22,110 --> 00:15:23,490
Yukio!

223
00:15:27,100 --> 00:15:29,080
Isso fede!

224
00:15:44,940 --> 00:15:46,440
Yukio?

225
00:15:46,440 --> 00:15:48,110
Hobgoblins.

226
00:15:48,110 --> 00:15:51,020
